ntal and unpredictable, to defy the logic of \"What you see is what you get\". Is the environment changing around you, or is it your imagination? Will jumping to your death kill you, or will it save you? Could the wrong answer actually turn out to be the right answer?\n\nIn Only If, you will fail a lot, you will die a lot, and you will undoubtedly be confused. Or will you?", "themes": [{"id": 17, "name": "Fantasy"}, {"id": 19, "name": "Horror"}, {"id": 43, "name": "Mystery"}], "url": "https://www.igdb.com/games/only-if", "videos": [{"id": 19931, "name": "Teaser", "video_id": "fvu7ko7ljXM", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fvu7ko7ljXM", "title": "Only if - Teaser Trailer", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/fvu7ko7ljXM/sddefault.jpg"}, {"id": 19932, "name": "Trailer", "video_id": "qs749jnwKBA", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qs749jnwKBA", "title": "Only if - I Dont Get It Trailer", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/qs749jnwKBA/maxresdefault.jpg"}, {"id": 19933, "name": "Launch Trailer", "video_id": "inB_5-BWsbM", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=inB_5-BWsbM", "title": "Only If - Launch Trailer", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/inB_5-BWsbM/maxresdefault.jpg"}, {"id": 19934, "name": "Beta Walkthrough", "video_id": "iXkzWgC8MnI", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iXkzWgC8MnI", "title": "Only if [Beta] Walkthrough", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/iXkzWgC8MnI/maxresdefault.jpg"}]}